title: 6 AM Hour - Dave's Trip to Disney
description:
We're trying it this way for today to see if it fixes the issue of having to have to go back into the app to go to the next episode! If it doesn't work or you still hate it, let us know! This will be the last day of testing this!

Dave returns to the show and talks about some of the stuff that happened in Disney, & More!
